headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting Charter Communications Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Charter Communications has underperformed the broader market over the past year, and analysts remain skeptical about the stock’s prospects.

headline: Netflix grants Warner Bros. Discovery 7-day waiver to reopen deal talks with Paramount Skydance
summary: Warner Bros. Discovery on Tuesday said it will engage in deal talks with Paramount Skydance under a 7-day waiver from Netflix.
